title: Live well in this studio close to downtown
posting_body: Stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, Farmhouse style sink, Custom Quartz Countertops & Islands in kitchen.
Wood-look flooring in kitchen, living room & bedrooms.
Black-out solar shades in each bedroom.
Pre-wired intrusion alarm systems & USB charging outlets.
Undoubtedly one of the most beautiful pools of any complex & direct access to a great hiking trail.
It's living like you're on vacation.
Stake your claim in the throbbing, hottest new area to live in Austin!
Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor
*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.
